/* Animation Properties */

/* animation-name 
animation-duration : time it lasts
animation-timing-function : comes fast/slow/steps
animation-delay: after how much time
animation-iteration-count : how many time iteration takes places 
animation-direction -normal(forward each cycle) , reverse (to-from) , alternate(to-form & from - to) , alternate-reverse*/



/*SHORTHAND - animation: colorAnime 2s ease-in 0s infinite normal; */

